      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELEGANTLY WRITTEN (5) was back to her best, posting her third win here over 1600m. Keeps the 1.5kg claim, and she rates to go on with the job. DESIGNER DREAMER (7) came from the back of the 11-horse field, beaten 0.9L in the same contest as the favourite. Doesn't have as many runners to get around today, and he's a decent chance to bounce. ZEWINNA (2) brings a 1.5L defeat here over 1400m in tougher grade. Has a handy 1.5kg claim and finally draws an inside gate. Well in the mix. SCARLETTI (6) came from well back on the corner to score last time out over 1650m at Devonport Synthetic. Didn't have the best of it at Hobart prior and will be around the mark.",
